{"type": "article", "id": 28543, "title": "茶滤系列", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-22T06:53:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 55, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702153147xaK0s2dEVYCFJmog.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>还记得我们之前介绍过的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/26601.html\">鸭嘴兽茶滤</a>吗？如果你更喜欢简单的造型，不妨来看看 Andrea Ponti 设计的 Ommo 系列。甜甜圈造型的 Torus 挂在杯沿上就可以泡出一杯茶饮，平时也可以用来储存茶叶，多个 Torus 还可以叠在支架上。另一款茶滤 Koma 则有着圆形的底座和细长的把手，可以用来在冲泡时进行搅拌，上方的金属盖只需要轻轻一按就可以控制开阖。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153144vC8g2rULDB4ul91h.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153145toKGq6uLlj5exrBm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153146zrMlgwqKatvV9FCY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153147VLFj40RUIczY1SQ3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}